m%20also%20does%20hairstyling%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20too.%20The%20celebrity%20hairdresser%20recently%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20charges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20revealing%20directly%2C%20how%20much%20he%20charged%20for%20Virat%20Kohli's%20hairstyle%2C%20Hakim%20gave%20an%20idea.%20%26quot%3BMy%20fee%20is%20very%20simple%20which%20everybody%20knows%20how%20much%20I%20charge.%20So%2C%20it%20starts%20from%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20That's%20the%20minimum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-KDEtdYqNdg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrut%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMahi%20sir%20and%20Virat%2C%20they%20are%20very%20old%20friends%20and%20they%20have%20been%20coming%20to%20me%20for%20haircuts%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20And%20since%20IPL%20was%20coming%20now%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20cool%20and%20different.%20And%20Virat%20always%20have%20references%20that%20'we%20need%20to%20try%20this%2C%20we%20will%20try%20that%20next%20time'%2C%26quot%3B%20Hakim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20about%20Virat%20Kohli's%20hairstyle%20for%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20keep%20chatting%20all%20the%20time%20that%20%C2%A0what%20should%20(be)%20the%20next%20look.%20This%20time%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20really%20cool.%20We%20did%20a%20slit%20in%20his%20eyebrows%20and%20kept%20the%20sides%20a%20little%20fade%2C%20a%20little%20mullet%20at%20the%20back.%20The%20texture%20can%20show%20and%20yeah%2C%20and%20we%20did%20a%20little%20colour%20in%20the%20hair.%20So%20when%20I%20posted%20the%20picture%2C%20it%20really%20broke%20the%20internet%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20shares%20and%20likes%20I%20got%20on%20my%20post%2C%20that%20was%20insane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20has%20an%20immense%20fan%20following.%20People%20follow%20Virat%20Kohli%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20And%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20a%20big%20sensation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fashion%20and%20aesthetics.%20His%20own%20aesthetics%20are%20so%20strong%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fashion.%20He%20is%20not%20only%20one%20of%20the%20best%20but%20he%20is%20the%20best%20player%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20also%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20style%2C%20fashion%2C%20he%20is%20number%20one.%20And%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20Dhoni%2C%20I%20visualize%20Mahi%20in%20a%20very%20different%20way.%20For%20me%2C%20he%20is%20not%20less%20than%20any%20Hollywood%20actor.%20I%20always%20visualize%20him%20as%20a%20star%2C%20as%20a%20cool%20guy.%20So%20whenever%20there%20is%20an%20ad%20film%20shoot%20happening%2C%20I%20always%20request%20him%2C%20'Let%20me%20record%20you%20or%20let%20me%20do%20some%20photo%20shoot%20from%20my%20phone.%20And%20then%20I'll%20post%20it%20later%20whenever%20I%20feel%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20has%20been%20RCB's%20only%20hope%20in%20this%20otherwise%20dull%20IPL%202024%20season%20so%20far.%20In%20four%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20203%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2067.66%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20almost%20141%2C%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%20His%20best%20score%20is%2083*.%20He%20is%20the%20Orange%20Cap%20holder%20in%20the%20season%20so%20far%20for%20most%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20some%20worrying%20trends%20about%20Virat%20that%20pop%20up%20everytime%20its%20time%20to%20take%20on%20Men%20in%20Pink.%20While%20the%20Sawai%20Mansingh%20Stadium%20has%20been%20extremely%20great%20for%20Virat%20as%20an%20international%20cricketer%2C%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20replicate%20his%20international%20numbers%20in%20IPL%20at%20this%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20three%20international%20games%20here%2C%20Virat%20has%20scored%20195%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2097.50%2C%20with%20a%20century%20and%20a%20fifty