ed%20by%20Jews%20in%20revolt%20against%20the%20Roman%20Empire.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20archeological%20discovery%20echoes%20some%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologists%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Funderground-hideout-nearly-2000-years-ago-unearthed-israel-2024-04-03%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael%20have%20uncovered%20a%20huge%20labyrinth%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20by%20Jewish%20rebels%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20Roman%20legions%2C%20Reuters%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20underground%20refuge%20in%20northern%20Israel%20was%20dug%20nearly%202%2C000%20years%20ago%20during%20a%20revolt%20against%20the%20Roman%20Empire.%20While%20the%20complex%20was%20first%20discovered%20decades%20ago%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20properly%20excavated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20archeological%20discovery%20echoes%20some%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ancient%20Jewish%20labyrinth%2C%20consisting%20of%20narrow%20tunnels%20and%20caves%20designed%20to%20shelter%20entire%20families%2C%20was%20found%20in%20Huqoq%20in%20Galilee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fprogram%2Fnewsfeed%2F2024%2F4%2F4%2Funderground-tunnels-found-in-israel-from-jewish-revolt-against-romans%23%3A~%3Atext%3DArchaeologists%2520have%2520uncovered%2520a%2520vast%2CEmpire%2527s%2520occupation%25202%252C000%2520years%2520ago.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20by%20Al%20Jazeera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uri%20Berger%20of%20the%20Israel%20Antiquities%20Authority%20said%20the%20network%20was%20dug%20%26quot%3Bfor%20families%20to%20hide%20while%20the%20Romans%20were%20here%2C%20because%20they%20feared%20for%20their%20lives%2C%20for%20their%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20amazed%20to%20see%20how%20big%20this%20complex%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Berger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Roman%20occupation%2C%20Jewis