%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline's%20CEO%2C%20Vinod%20Kannan%2C%20also%20apologised%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20customers%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20some%20pilots%20have%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20contract.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20light%20of%20the%20recent%20disruptions%20in%20our%20network%20owing%20to%20various%20operational%20reasons%2C%20we%20acknowledge%20and%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20inconvenience%20this%20has%20caused%20to%20our%20customers.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20again%20clarify%20that%20these%20disruptions%20were%20due%20to%20the%20cascading%20effect%20of%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors...%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20inconvenience%20this%20has%20caused%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20sincerely%20apologise%20to%20them%20for%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20full-service%20carrier%20has%20adequate%20crew%20for%20normal%20operations%2C%20Mr%20Kannan%20said%20the%20airline%20was%20challenged%20because%20it%20was%20operating%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20high%20utilisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20addressing%20this%20on%20a%20war%20footing.%20Hence%2C%20we%20are%20continuing%20to%20hire%20more%20pilots%20and%20are%20also%20carefully%20scaling%20back%20our%20operations%20slightly%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20resilience%2C%20and%20a%20buffer%20in%20the%20rosters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20customer%20front%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20deployed%20larger%20aircraft%20like%20our%20B787-9%20Dreamliner%20and%20A321neo%20aircraft%20on%20select%20domestic%20routes%20to%20accommodate%20more%20customers%2C%20wherever%20possible.%20Furthermore%2C%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20all%20customers%20affected%20by%20the%20delays%20and%20cancellations%20over%20the%20last%20weekend%2C%20to%20offer%20relevant%20refunds%20and%20compensation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kannan%20claimed%20that%20the%20airline's%20on-time%20performance%20has%20improved%20in%20the%20past%20three%20days%20and%20said%20that%20it%20hoped%20to%20stabilise%20its%20operations%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20April%20by%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20reference%20to%20concerns%20being%20raised%20regarding%20the%20new%20pay%20structure%20of%20our%20pilots%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20over%2098%25%20of%20pilots%20have%20signed%20the%20new%20contract.%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20we%20are%20aware%20that%20some%20pilots%20have%20some%20concerns%20and%20queries%20regarding%20the%20contract.%20We%20are%20engaging%20with%20them%20to%20clarify%20and%20resolve%20the%20same.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20not%20caused%20any%20visible%20spike%20in%20attrition%20amongst%20pilots%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carrier%20had%20cancelled%20over%20125%20flights%20in%20three%20days%20starting%20Monday%20and%20pilots%20have%20said%20that%20they%20are%20flying%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bedge%20of%20their%20maximum%20flight%20duty%20limitations%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20was%20causing%20major%20health%20issues%20and%20leading%20to%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20falling%20sick%20frequently%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20salary%20structure%20ahead%20of%20the%20airline's%20merger%20with%20Air%20India%20-%20both%20brands%20are%20under%20the%20Tata%20stable%20-%20has%20also%20caused%20consternation%20among%20the%20pilots.%20Under%20the%20new%20structure%2C%20salaries%20of%20junior%20co-pilots%20will%20go%20down%20from%20Rs%202.35%20lakh%20per%20month%20to%20Rs%201.88%20lakh%20because%20they%20will%20be%20mandated%20to%20fly%20only%2040%20hours%20instead%20of%20the%20earlier%2070.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20said%20those%20who%20opted%20to%20fly%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20hours%20could%20earn%20even%20more%20than%20they%20made%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pub