or%2C%20On%20Treatment%20For%20South%20Chennai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamilisai%20Soundararajan%2C%20the%20BJP's%20South%20Chennai%20candidate%2C%20faces%20a%20huge%20electoral%20battle%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20has%20been%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20at%20present%20represented%20by%20Tamilachi%20Thangapandian.%20She%20also%20faces%20AIADMK's%20J%20Jayavardhan%2C%20hence%20making%20this%20year's%20contest%20a%20triangular%20one%20with%20all%20three%20leaders%20popular%20among%20large%20sections%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20I%20can%20lead%20this%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Soundararajan%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview.%20She%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20giving%20her%20an%20opportunity%20to%20fight%20from%20South%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20change.%20I%20want%20to%20create%20good%20infrastructure%20in%20South%20Chennai.%20I%20have%20been%20a%20voter%20for%20decades%20from%20here.%20I%20know%20each%20and%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20in%20this%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Soundararajan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20had%20given%20up%20governorship%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20doctor%2C%20on%20what%20medicine%20she%20would%20give%20to%20South%20Chennai%2C%20Ms%20Soundararajan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20constituency%20is%20full%20of%20rubbish%20and%20dumping%20yards.%20The%20immunity%20of%20the%20constituency%20needs%20to%20be%20improved.%20And%20then%20look%20into%20transport%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20mosquito%20menace%2C%20no%20infrastructure...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20diagnose%20the%20disease%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Soundararajan%20task%20won't%20be%20easy.%20Winning%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20been%20historically%20a%20task%20that's%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Ms%20Soundararajan%2C%20however%2C%20said%20she%20is%20confident%20she%20can%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20alliance%20with%20the%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%20(PMK)%20gives%20it%20an%20opening%2C%20as%20the%20PMK%20has%20electoral%20heft%20in%20the%20northern%20region%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20where%20the%20Vanniyars%2C%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20(MBCs)%2C%20are%20key%20in%20deciding%20the%20fate%20of%20candidates%20in%20a%20number%20of%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Soundararajan%20said%20the%20key%20to%20winning%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20to%20ensure%20people%20understand%20the%20alignment%20of%20national%20and%20state%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Chennai%20constituency%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20on%20April%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712414100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fb6mu49lo_tamilsai_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjps-tamilisai-soundararajan-a-doctor-on-treatment-for-south-chennai-5388483%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%2C%20the%20BJP's%20South%20Chennai%20candidate%2C%20faces%20a%20huge%20electoral%20battle%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20has%20been%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20at%20present%20represented%20by%20Tamilachi%20Thangapandian.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjps-tamilisai-soundararajan-a-doctor-on-treatment-for-south-chennai-5388483%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjps-tamilisai-soundararajan-a-doctor-on-treatment-for-south-chennai-5388483%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-202