and%20asked%20if%20we%20can%20have%20a%20PT%20period%20on%20our%20free%20period.%20The%20teacher%20gave%20us%20permission.%20I%20became%20so%20excited%20that%20I%20went%20shouting%20across%20the%20corridors.%20My%20classmates%20enjoyed%20the%20free%20period%2C%20but%20I%20was%20punished%20for%20shouting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20go%20to%20the%20church%20with%20my%20family%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%20Then%20my%20mom%20would%20cook%20something%20special%20on%20Sundays.%20I%20used%20to%20help%20her%20by%20finishing%20what%20she%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Samson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Samson%20is%20currently%20leading%20RR%20in%20the%20ongoing%20season%20of%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20captain%20Sanju%20Samson%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bowl%20against%20Faf%20du%20Plessis-led%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20in%20their%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20here%20at%20Sawai%20Mansingh%20Stadium%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERR%20heads%20into%20the%20game%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20victory%20against%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20while%20RCB%20suffered%20a%20defeat%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20in%20its%20previous%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20one%20victory%20in%20four%20matches%2C%20RCB%20are%20currently%20in%20the%208th%20position%20in%20the%2010-team%20table%20which%20fairly%20indicates%20their%20troubles%20while%20Rajasthan's%20all-win%20record%20so%20far%20placed%20them%20on%20the%20second%20spot%20with%20six%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712413080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fqc5beag8_sanju-samson-bcci_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwas-punished-for-sanju-samson-recalls-unheard-tale-ahead-of-rrs-game-vs-rcb-5387699%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sanju%20Samson%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in