ing%20given%20that%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Meta's%20CEO%2C%20is%20married%20to%20a%20woman%20of%20East%20Asian%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Chan%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Chinese%20immigrants%20to%20America%2C%20met%20Zuckerberg%20whilst%20studying%20at%20Harvard.%20The%20couple%20married%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20took%20to%20X%20to%20share%20pictures%20of%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Chan%2C%20joking%20that%20they%20had%20successfully%20managed%20to%20create%20the%20images%20using%20Imagine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTilqw2Uwdu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTilqw2Uwdu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Khalid%20Natto%20%E2%98%95%EF%B8%8F%20Na2%20Perspective%20Podcast%20%E2%98%95%EF%B8%8F%20(%40ChairmanNatto)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChairmanNatto%2Fstatus%2F1775590214200672696%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Verge%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F4%2F3%2F24120029%2Finstagram-meta-ai-sticker-generator-asian-people-racism%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efirst%20reported%20the%20issue%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20reporter%20Mia%20Sato%20claimed%20she%20tried%20%26quot%3Bdozens%20of%20times%26quot%3B%20to%20create%20images%20of%20Asian%20men%20and%20women%20with%20white%20partners%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESato%20said%20the%20image%20generator%20was%20only%20able%20to%20return%20one%20accurate%20image%20of%20the%20races%20specified%20in%20her%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20by%20no%20means%20the%20first%20major%20tech%20company%20that%20has%20been%20blasted%20for%20%26quot%3Bracist%26quot%3B%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Google%20was%20forced%20to%20pause%20its%20Gemini%20image%20generator%20after%20users%20found%20it%20was%20creating%20historically%20inaccurate%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20found%20that%20the%20image%20generator%20would%20produce%20pictures%20of%20Asian%20Nazis%20in%201940%20Germany%2C%20black%20Vikings%20or%20even%20female%20medieval%20knights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20company%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20overly%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGoogle_Comms%2Fstatus%2F1760603321944121506%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BGemini's%20AI%20image%20generation%20does%20generate%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20people.%20And%20that's%20generally%20a%20good%20thing%20because%20people%20around%20the%20world%20use%20it.%20But%20it's%20missing%20the%20mark%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20AI's%20racial%20prejudices%20have%20long%20been%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr%20Nakeema%20Stefflbauer%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20AI%20ethics%20and%20CEO%20of%20women%20in%20tech%20network%20Frauenloop%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-discrimination-bias-worse-problem-than-sentience-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3BWhen%20predictive%20algorithms%20or%20so-called%20'AI'%20are%20so%20widely%20used%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20recognise%20that%20these%20predictions%20are%20often%20based%20on%20little%20more%20than%20rapid%20regurgitation%20of%20crowdsourced%20opinions%2C%20stereotypes%2C%20or%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quo