ppier-despite-higher-costs-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20of%20five%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20my%20husband%2C%20my%20three%20daughters%2C%20and%20I%20arrived%20in%20March%20of%202012%2C%20we%20were%20more%20than%20happy%20with%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-costs-to-buy-a-2-bedroom-flat-by-country-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-bedroom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one-and-a-half-bath%20apartment%2C%20which%20came%20with%20a%20dishwasher.%20In%20all%2C%20the%20place%20was%20950%20square%20feet.%20It%20was%20especially%20great%20because%20we%20lived%20near%20good%20schools%2C%20and%20it%20was%20in%20a%20very%20safe%20area.%20Plus%2C%20the%20apartment%20was%20in%20a%20gated%20building%20with%20a%20parking%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20this%20apartment%20worked%20for%20us.%20But%20then%20another%20baby%20came%2C%20and%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-divorced-multigenerational-home-safe-haven-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20continued%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20added%20two%20people%20to%20our%20family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20LA%2C%20my%20aunt%20visited%20from%20Chicago%20frequently%20because%20she%20loved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorce-share-custody-kids-parenting-plan-time-regret-decision-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20time%20with%20my%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20they%20were%20little%20and%20adored%20her%2C%20too.%20As%20time%20went%20on%20and%20my%20aunt%20got%20older%2C%20she%20retired.%20We%20invited%20her%20to%20live%20with%20us%2C%20even%20though%20she%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202017%2C%20I%20had%20my%204th%20child%2C%20a%20son.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20had%20three%20teenagers%20and%20a%20toddler%20living%20in%20the%20apartment.%20In%20early%202020%2C%20my%20aunt%20had%20been%20visiting%20us%20for%20a%20while%20and%20hadn't%20set%20a%20date%20to%20return%20to%20Chicago%20yet%3B%20then%20she%20got%20stuck%20here.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20we%20weren't%20sure%20when%20and%20if%20she%20was%20going%20back%20to%20Chicago.%20We%20discussed%20giving%20up%20her%20apartment%20and%20moving%20to%20California%20for%20good%20as%20she%20was%20getting%20up%20there%20in%20age.%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20her%20living%20on%20her%20own%20as%20health%20problems%20began%20to%20arise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20then%20had%20time%20off%20from%20work%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20That%20meant%20the%20seven%20of%20us%20were%20stuck%20in%20our%20950-square-foot%20apartment%20%E2%80%94%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomeschool-kids-travel-family-benefits-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeschooling%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20three%20oldest%20kids%20with%20a%203%20year%20old%20running%20around.%20It%20wasn't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20constantly%20felt%20overwhelmed%20and%20had%20a%20great%20lack%20of%20privacy.%20My%20husband%2C%20son%2C%20and%20I%20shared%20a%20king-sized%20bed%20in%20our%20small%20bedroom%2C%20while%20my%20three%20teens%20shared%20the%20second%20bedroom.%20My%20aunt%20got%20the%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20solace%20was%20my%20desk%20with%20my%20computer%2C%20where%20I%20would%20play%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaldur-gate-3-larian-studios-sequel-dlc-new-content-staff-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20games%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20write%20to%20take%20my%20mind%20off%20the%20fear%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20outside%20world.%20To%20say%20I%20was%20stressed%20out%20was%20an%20understatement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20move%20out%2C%20but%20we%20decided%20to%20redecorate%20instead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202021%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20move%2C%20which%20was%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20We%20currently%20pay%20%242%2C100%20a%20month%20for%20our%20apartment%2C%20but%20we%20realized%20that%20if%20we%20wanted%20a%20bigger%20place%20in%20LA%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20pay%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20a%20new%20place%20during%20the%20pandemic%20was%20another%20bag%20of%20problems.%20Many%20places%20were%20holding%20crowded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-rent-apartments-prices-soaring-competition-millennial-gen-z-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20houses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20we%20tried%20to%20avoid.%20It%20seemed%20like%20everyone%20was%20trying%20to%20move%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20It%20was%20impossible%3B%20we%20couldn't%20find%20the%20right%20place%20for%20us.%20Many%20places%20seemed%20to%20frown%20when%20we%20told%20them%20we%20were%20a%20family%20of%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lots%20of%20looking%2C%20we%20finally%20gave%20in%20and%20decided%20to%20stay%20put%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20With%20more%20free%20time%20around%20the%20house%20when%20the%20pandemic%20let%20up%2C%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-brooklyn-apartment-rent-renvation-before-after-photos-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecorating%20and%20remodeling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20ordered%20new%20furniture%20and%20housewares.%20The%20older%20kids%20were%20disappointed%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20moving%20but%20were%20willing%20to%20help%20reorganize%20and%20redecorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20with%20the%20three%20teenagers.%20Having%20three%20kids%20in%20a%20bedroom%20is%20never%20ideal%2C%20but%20thankfully%2C%20they%20all%20get%20along%20well.%20We%20bought%20a%20new%20bunkbed%2C%20and%20the%20oldest%20child%20got%20a%20loft%20bed%20with%20a%20desk%20at%20the%20bottom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20continued%20to%20share%20a%20bedroom%20with%20us%2C%20but%20on%20his%207th%20birthday%2C%20we%20got%20him%20his%20own%20bed%2C%20which%20he%20was%20excited%20about.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20bought%20ourselves%20a%20new%20bed%20frame.%20I%20then%20transformed%20the%20bedroom%20into%20the%20cottage%20core%20room%20of%20my%20dreams.%20I%20hung%20fake%20flowers%2C%20vintage%20postcards%2C%20and%20frames%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-k-pop-songs-this-year-ranked-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EK-pop%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20my%20aunt%20got%20a%20comfy%20reclining%20chair%20and%20a%20bed%20in%20the%20living%20room.%20After%20a%20certain%20time%20of%20night%2C%20the%20living%20room%20becomes%20her%20bedroom.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20also%20bought%20two%20new%20sofas%20for%20family%20movie%20nights%20that%20we%20could%20all%20fit%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20still%20looking%20to%20move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20occasionally%20have%20issues%20with%20only%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20but%20we%20remind%20our%20kids%20that%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20grew%20up%20with%20one%20bathroom%20and%20several%20siblings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20planning%20on%20moving.%20We%20look%20at%20rentals%20from%20time%20to%20time%20when%20something%20good%20comes%20up%20on%20Zillow.%20We%20have%20even%20seriously%20discussed%20moving%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-la-california-from-vancouver-canada-rent-health-care-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20our%20rent%20continues%20to%20go%20up.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20we're%20staying%20put%20and%20making%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarge-family-live-two-bedroom-apartment-los-angeles-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712410021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66102a643f923f7dab0511ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%2