sh%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fselena-gomez-and-benny-blancos-romance-is-turning-very-serious-report%2Farticleshow%2F109091082.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChinese%20In%20Pak%20Do%20Not%20Want%20To%20Follow%20Security%20Discipline%26quot%3B%3A%20Maryam%20Nawaz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaryam%20Nawaz%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Pakistan's%20Punjab%20province%2C%C2%A0on%20Friday%20said%20that%20Chinese%20nationals%20living%20in%20Pakistan%20get%20%26quot%3Bresentful%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20are%20asked%20to%20follow%20security%20protocols.%20Her%20remarks%20came%20a%20week%20after%20five%20Chinese%20engineers%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20suicide%20bombing%20in%20the%20restive%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryam%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20three-time%20former%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20became%20the%20first-ever%20woman%20chief%20minister%20of%20a%20province%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20while%20addressing%20her%20maiden%20Apex%20Committee%20meeting%20here%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Chinese%20living%20here%20do%20not%20want%20to%20follow%20security%20discipline%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20resentful%20when%20they%20are%20asked%20to%20follow%20security%20protocols.%20They%20don't%20want%20to%20come%20under%20any%20discipline%20as%20they%20fret%20over%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Corps%20Commander%20Lahore%20Lt%20Gen%20Syed%20Aamer%20Raza%20and%20other%20senior%20military%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryam%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20her%20government's%20resolve%20to%20provide%20fool-proof%20security%20to%20the%20Chinese%20nationals%20working%20on%20development%20projects%20in%20the%20Punjab%20province.%20The%20meeting%20also%20condemned%20the%20killing%20of%20Chinese%20engineers%20in%20Bisham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Chinese%20engineers%20and%20their%20Pakistani%20driver%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20suicide%20bombing%20last%20week%20while%20travelling%20between%20Islamabad%20and%20a%20hydroelectric%20dam%20construction%20site%20in%20Dasu%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20The%20bus%20was%20attacked%20in%20Bisham%20city%20of%20Shangla%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryam%20said%20terrorism%20has%20taken%20the%20shape%20of%20difficult%20warfare.%20%26quot%3BTerrorists%20got%20digitalised%20and%20we%20need%20to%20be%20ahead%20of%20them%20on%20such%20platforms.%20Besides%2C%20terrorists%20have%20the%20latest%20weapons%20and%20technology.%20They%20have%20the%20US%20weapons%20which%20they%20got%20in%20Afghanistan.%20The%20weapons%20coming%20from%20Afghanistan%20are%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2050-year-old%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20party%20leader%20added%20that%20the%20youth%20are%20also%20being%20brainwashed%20and%20recruited%20by%20terrorists.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20social%20media%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20tools%20being%20used%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maryam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20on%20Friday%20directed%20all%20the%20security%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20fool-proof%20security%20arrangements%20for%20the%20Chinese%20nationals%20working%20on%20various%20projects%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpersonally%20review%20the%20meetings%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20overall%20security%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Chinese%20citizens%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20said%20the%20war%20against%20the%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20will%20continue%20till%20its%20complete%20eradication%20from%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20p