0that%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%202030%2C%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%24500%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pif.gov.sa%2Fen%2Four-investments%2Fgiga-projects%2Fneom%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeom%3C%2Fa%3E%20megacity%2C%20which%20will%20cover%2026%2C500%20square%20kilometers%20(just%20over%2010%2C200%20square%20miles)%2C%20is%20part%20of%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman's%20Vision%202030%20plan%20to%20diversify%20the%20kingdom's%20economy%20away%20from%20oil%20and%20pivot%20toward%20tech%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Neom%20is%20just%20one%20of%20several%20%26quot%3Bgigaprojects%26quot%3B%20underway%20as%20part%20of%20this%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20Public%20Investment%20Fund%20(PIF)%2C%20its%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%2C%20has%20long%20shouldered%20the%20large%20financial%20burden%20imposed%20by%20such%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20estimated%20to%20run%20at%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20PIF%20said%20in%20January%20that%20its%20cash%20as%20of%20September%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-borrowing-help-fund-megaprojects-oil-prices-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20lowest%20level%20since%20December%202020%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20has%20forced%20the%20government%20to%20turn%20to%20a%20tactic%20it%20hasn't%20used%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20boost%20its%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20borrowing%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20that%20the%20kingdom%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fsaudi-arabia-transfers-8-aramco-pif-portfolio-spa-reports-2024-03-07%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSaudi%2520Arabia%2520is%2520poised%2520to%2Cshares%2520would%2520be%2520t