ps%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-tesla-most-popular-stock-retail-investors-daytraders-nvda-tsla-2024-3%5C%22%3Etop%20stock%20pick%20among%20retail%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20chipmaker's%20monster-sized%20gains%20could%20soon%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20according%20to%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20analyst%20at%20DA%20Davidson.%20He's%20calling%20for%20as%20much%20as%20a%2020%25%20slide%20in%20Nvidia%20stock%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20joining%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20strategists%20who%20are%20skeptical%20of%20Nvidia's%20dizzying%20stock%20market%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20unlikely%20to%20keep%20up%20its%20rapid%20pace%20of%20growth%2C%20as%20companies%20investing%20in%20AI%20are%20bound%20to%20tap%20out%20eventually%2C%20Luria%20said%2C%20speaking%20recently%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnnbloomberg.ca%2Ftechnology%2Fvideo%2Fnvidia-could-fall-more-than-20-analyst~2843170%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBNN%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20note%2C%20he%20assigned%20a%20%26quot%3Bhold%26quot%3B%20rating%20to%20the%20stock%20and%20a%20price%20target%20of%20%24620%2C%20the%20lowest%20estimate%20on%20Wall%20Street.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20its%20big%20customers%20%E2%80%A6%20are%20stocking%20up%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-chips-ai-commodity-graphcore-alternative-2023-9%5C%22%3EGPU%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Nvidia's%20biggest%20AI%20chip%20buyers%2C%20like%20Microsoft%20and%20Amazon.%20%26quot%3BBut%20as%20they%20get%20to%20the%20capacity%20that%20they%20need%20to%20have%2C%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20keep%20buying%20this%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20which%20is%20what%20current%20Nvidia%20estimates%20imply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20earnings%20per%20share%20soar%20to%20%2424.75