urrounding%20concealment%20can%20be%20enough%20to%20be%20effective.%20It's%20about%20mastering%20disappearing%20in%20depth%20and%20shadows%20in%20your%20environment.%20That's%20something%20we%20have%20to%20learn%20as%20snipers%20that%20sets%20us%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20else%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-sniper-describes-record-longest-kill-shot-claim-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erange%20estimation%20and%20being%20able%20to%20detect%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20trainable.%20And%20we%20can%20practice%20that%20at%20any%20time.%20But%20being%20good%20in%20the%20field%20and%20being%20self-sustainable%20is%20probably%20more%20valuable%20than%20just%20being%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20a%20distance%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20with%20drones%2C%20our%20main%20job%20is%20to%20train%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-is-how-close-a-sniper-can-get-without-detection-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremain%20hidden%20from%20all%20adversaries%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20still%20maintaining%20freedom%20of%20maneuver%20and%20eyes%20on%20the%20objective.%20So%20that's%20why%20fieldcraft%20is%20so%20important%2C%20that's%20why%20we%20harp%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFelt%20like%20we%20needed%20to%20earn%20our%20spot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20U.S.%20Army%20Ranger%20from%20the%2075th%20Ranger%20Regiment%20pull%20security%20during%20Joint%20Pacific%20Multinational%20Readiness%20Center%2024-02%20at%20Donnelly%20Training%20Area%2C%20Alaska%2C%20Feb%2012%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66103bf11caec1275a6d5690%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20U.S.%20Army%20Ranger%20from%20the%2075th%20Ranger%20Regiment%20pull%20security%20during%20Joint%20Pacific%20Multinational%20Readiness%20Center%2024-02%20at%20Donnelly%20Training%20Area%2C%20Alaska%2C%20Feb%2012%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20photo%20by%20Spc.%20Wyatt%20Moore%20%2F%2028th%20Public%20Affairs%20Detachment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20the%20Army%20because%20I%20am%20a%20first-generation%20American.%20My%20family's%20from%20Korea%2C%20so%20I%20felt%20like%20somewhere%20along%20the%20lines%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20earn%20our%20spot%20in%20the%20country%20by%20serving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20enlisted%2C%20I%20thought%20being%20a%20sniper%20was%20more%20of%20a%20pipe%20dream%20than%20anything.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20snipers%20that%20I%20saw%20as%20a%20junior%20enlisted%20soldier%20were%20the%20rock%20stars%20of%20our%20battalion.%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20could%20be%20part%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20after%20a%20training%20rotation%20overseas%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20by%20my%20former%20team%20leader%20to%20try%20out%20for%20recon.%20And%20then%2C%20I%20got%20first-hand%20experience%2C%20and%20realized%20I%20could%20do%20it.%20Then%20I%20tried%20out%20for%20sniping%20and%20was%20picked.%20The%20opportunity%20just%20kind%20of%20presented%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20deployed%20to%20Iraq%20in%202019%20in%20support%20of%20Operation%20Inherent%20Resolve%2C%20the%20international%20fight%20against%20the%20Islamic%20State.%20We%20were%20primarily%20attached%20to%20our%20scouts%20and%20partook%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20operations%2C%20mainly%20overwatch%2C%20key%20leader%20engagements%2C%20dismounted%20operations%2C%20and%20base%20security.%20It%20was%20pretty%20standard%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Staff%20Sergeant%20Phillip%20Cho%20firing%20a%20rifle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66102e0c1caec1275a6d4d70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22730%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESSG%20Cho%20said%20fieldcraft%20is%20the%20most%20challenging%20and%20important%20part%20of%20being%20a%20sniper.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sergeant%20Phillip%20Cho%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20serving%20in%20the%20Arctic%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-us-army-is-training-soldiers-to-fight-in-arctic-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrain%20presents%20a%20unique%20set%20of%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20which%20snipers%20have%20to%20be%20prepared.%20Any%20failure%20in%20planning%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-in-alaskas-tundra-prepare-against-russia-and-china-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecause%20cold%20weather%20injuries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20environments%2C%20water%20is%20a%20priority.%20But%20you%20can't%20just%20eat%20snow%20because%20it%20will%20lower%20your%20body%20temperature%2C%20and%20you%20can't%20always%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edrink%20glacier%20water%20because%20it%20isn't%20necessarily%20clean.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20lug%20fuel%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Earound%20with%20us%20to%20heat%20the%20water%2C%20and%20we%20usually%20carry%20a%20tent%2C%20just%20for%20safety%20from%20the%20elements.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20packed%20into%20a%20sled%2C%20and%20we%20pull%20it%20for%20miles%20and%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20there%20were%20challenges.%20We%20had%20to%20have%20water%20there%20too.%20But%20our%20vehicles%20were%20constantly%20working.%20They%20didn't%20have%20to%20work%20harder%20like%20they%20do%20in%20the%20cold.%20Our%20equipment%20wasn't%20failing.%20The%20conditions%20were%20not%20slowing%20us%20down.%20The%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20move%20in%20the%20Arctic%20is%20always%20about%20twice%20as%20long%20as%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eanticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20snipers%2C%20we%20have%20to%20carry%20a%20ton%20of%20extra%20equipment.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20our%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20observation%20and%20communication%20equipment%2C%20extra%20batteries%2C%20and%20the%20actual%20weapon%20and%20ammunition%20%E2%80%94%20is%20roughly%20around%2060%20to%2080%20pounds.%20In%20the%20winter%2C%20we%20need%20our%20bunny%20boots%2C%20different%20layers%20to%20keep%20us%20warm%2C%20and%20other%20extreme%20cold%20weather%20equipment%20that%20adds%20to%20that.%20Snipers%20are%20typically%20carrying%20anything%20from%2090%20to%20120%20pounds%20of%20extra%20weight%20in%20the%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arctic%20can%20be%20an%20insatiable%20beast%20and%20chews%20up%20some%20of%20the%20strongest%20soldiers%20that%20I've%20seen.%20But%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-breeding-new-kind-of-arctic-warrior-freezing-alaska-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrive%20in%20it%20like%20any%20other%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-sniper-arctic-biggest-challenge-isnt-shooting-its-hiding-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712403901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66102e1416bde8d4ead61e60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-sniper-arctic-biggest-challenge-isnt-shooting-its-hiding-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20fight%20in%20the%20unforgiving%20Arctic%2C%20US%20Army%20snipers%20take%20lessons%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Death%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Winter%20War.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-sniper-arctic-biggest-challenge-isnt-shooting-its-hiding-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20says%20truce%20talks%20on%2C%20after%20Gaza%20aid%20worker%20death%20outcry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22