moved%20towards%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20vermicompost%2C%20a%20biogas%20unit%20and%20hydroponics.%20Unable%20to%20cultivate%20enough%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle%2C%20hydroponic%20maize%20production%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20gamechanger%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20he%20has%20been%20using%20this%20method%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%20his%20livestock.%20What%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20it%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20grows%20it%20in%20his%20cupboard!%20He%20uses%20the%20soilless%20hydroponic%20method%20to%20grow%20maize%20fodder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%202018%2C%20he%20received%20the%20Haldhar%20Organic%20farmer%20award%20from%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20along%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Innovative%20farmer%20award%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20a%20farmer%20practising%20traditional%20farming%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20move%20to%20organic%20methods%20and%20find%20success%20in%20them%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20his%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20attempt%20to%20save%20soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20has%20been%20practicing%20organic%20farming%20since%202008%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan