20groundnuts%2C%20and%20vegetables.%20He%20also%20practises%20integrated%20farming%2C%20a%20sustainable%20agricultural%20system%20where%20crops%2C%20livestock%2C%20aquaculture%2C%20poultry%20are%20managed%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%20crops%2C%20he%20also%20manages%20livestock%2C%20including%20cows%2C%20goats%2C%20ducks%20and%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20he%20started%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20he%20got%20his%20soil%20tested.%20The%20test%20indicated%20that%20the%20soil%20was%20not%20healthy%2C%20and%20had%20rising%20pH%20levels%20and%20was%20getting%20spoilt.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20time%20when%20his%20turmeric%20crop%20was%20affected%20by%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20uses%20innovative%20methods%20of%20farming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20uses%20innovative%20methods%20of%20farming%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20at%20the%20KVK%20suggested%20some%20biofertilisers%20to%20salvage%20the%20turmeric%20crop%2C%20and