%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-5-1711769343.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346015%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi-based%20Aakash%20Maan%20co-founded%20%E2%80%98Volunteer%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20to%20establish%20volunteer%20tourism%20and%20help%20small%20businesses%20flourish%2C%20preventing%20rural%20migration.%20Currently%2C%20he%20has%20an%20army%20of%20around%202%2C000%20active%20volunteers%20helping%20put%20rural%20homestays%20on%20the%20tourism%20map.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346015%2Fvolunteer-tourism-yatra-aakash-maan-unique-travel-experiences-help-rural-homestays%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Grandma%E2%80%99s%20Traditional%20Rasam%20Powder%20Recipe%20Gave%20Birth%20to%20a%20Brand%20Earning%20Rs%2016%20Cr%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20began%20with%20a%20chance%20conversation%20between%20M%20S%20Ravindra%2C%20his%20wife%20Nagaratna%20Ravindra%2C%20and%20their%20relative%20Malathi%20Sharma%20in%202009.%20Ravindra%20had%20recently%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20General%20Mills%20and%20taken%20to%20agriculture%20full-time%2C%20while%20Nagaratna%20and%20Malathi%20were%20working%20their%20full-time%20jobs%20in%20Bengaluru.%20During%20this%20conversation%2C%20Ravindra%20spoke%20of%20his%20travels%20around%20India%20while%20working%20for%20General%20Mills%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20missing%20his%20native%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20(from%20South-Western%20Karnataka)%20and%20expressing%20his%20desire%20to%20take%20this%20unique%20culinary%20tradition%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20fate%20would%20have%20it%2C%20my%20aunt%20(Malathi)%20and%20parents%20(Ravindra%20and%20Nagaratna)%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20recipe%20to%20make%20small%20b