Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CSankethi%20cuisine%20is%20an%20eclectic%20blend%20of%20cultures%20and%20tastes%20from%20three%20diverse%20states%20%E2%80%94%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20The%20cuisine%20is%20known%20for%20dishes%20that%20are%20light%20on%20the%20palette%2C%20flavourful%2C%20and%20packed%20with%20nutritional%20wellness.%20The%20mainstay%20of%20this%20cuisine%20is%20characterised%20by%20the%20use%20of%20local%20ingredients%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287953%2Fgurugram-woman-quits-job-odisha-village-sustainable-cooking-practices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%20techniques%2C%20and%20authentic%20flavour%20profiles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20fascinating%20is%20the%20use%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20grains%2C%20lentils%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20spices%2C%20reflecting%20the%20agricultural%20abundance%20of%20their%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20beauty%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20lies%20in%20its%20rich%20diversity.%20While%20the%20recipes%20across%20households%20may%20share%20a%20common%20foundation%2C%20each%20final%20dish%20carries%20its%20own%20unique%20essence.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20hint%20of%20jaggery%20or%20a%20touch%20of%20asafoetida%2C%20perhaps%20some%20zesty%20tamarind%20for%20an%20added%20kick%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20these%20subtle%20variations%20that%20distinguish%20one%20household%E2%80%99s%20creation%20from%20another.%20It%20is%20the%20minute%20intricacies%20like%20the%20proportion%20of%20spices%2C%20duration%2C%20and%20temperature%20of%20roasting%2C%20and%20when%20they%20are%20removed%20from%20the%20flame%2C%20that%20contribute%20to%20robust%20flavours%20that%20infuse%20the%20cuisine%20with%20distinctive%20tastes%2C%20showcasing%20the%20unique%20selling%20point%20of%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20%3Ca%20re